{"tid":794161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赤膊男持武士刀斬傷人","createTime":"2018-08-26T03:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T04:50:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"659a7b1430ed5bad6df4fb0e11a39e80c87418f1","tid":794161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180826/20484953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F20484953&d=Ffc2IM8%2B%2BBCfU1b%2BtQePjr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=13a1421b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F20484953&h=5b062673\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180826/20484953</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月26日 <br />\n<br />\n赤膊男持武士刀斬傷人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/a0405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2Fa0405a.gif&h=3b8fbcba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方把赤膊男拘捕（左圖），武士刀掉在地上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名赤膊男昨午手持武士刀，闖入深水埗一間輪胎舖要求店東為武士刀開鋒，遭店東拒絕後突然拿起武士刀亂劈，斬傷店東腳部後逃走，街坊協助尾隨追截，合力制服疑兇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n空手道教練助追截<br />\n<br />\n現場是界限街一間輪胎舖，43歲姓賴東主稱，昨午3時許一名赤膊男用衫遮着手上一把約30吋長武士刀，來到店前亮刀說：「幫我磨咗佢吖，開光呀。」賴見對方語無倫次，回應：「我哋冇磨刀，你去第二度啦！」未料疑兇即在店內打開抽櫃查看有否財物，更拿去賴一頂帽後離去。<br />\n<br />\n賴立即追出店外喝止對方，疑兇突然發難說：「你係咪想死呀？」並手起刀落狂劈。賴大驚取來雨傘擋格，身旁的妻子見狀拿起摺凳替他擋刀，混亂中賴的右小腿被劈中受傷，疑兇傷人後逃走。<br />\n<br />\n在對面經營食肆的黃先生目擊事件，即協助追截兇徒。身兼空手道教練的黃指當時與朋友在店內，看到疑兇「拎住把刀揈嚟揈去，即刻跑去幫手，佢一路走，一路指住車路嘅司機叫佢哋停車，仲擰轉身作狀想斬我哋」。<br />\n<br />\n途人爭相走避，3人追至石硤尾街附近將疑人按在地上制服。警員趕至，以涉嫌普通襲擊及藏有攻擊性武器拘捕該名39歲姓甘男子。疑兇額頭受傷，被黑布蒙頭送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎家駒  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n虐死B案　母獲准保釋辦後事<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n的士司機燒炭　失控撞七人車"},{"pid":"ad90c7c29037425a3d3bfa2d15e255812fceec0e","tid":794161,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/left4dead/images/9/9a/Nickhardrainkatana.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20170912171912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fleft4dead%2Fimages%2F9%2F9a%2FNickhardrainkatana.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20170912171912&h=d834edb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66fbf52cb47d2d6e38d7961cba941af4ee1befc3","tid":794161,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad90c7c29037425a3d3bfa2d15e255812fceec0e","tid":794161,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/left4dead/images/9/9a/Nickhardrainkatana.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20170912171912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fleft4dead%2Fimages%2F9%2F9a%2FNickhardrainkatana.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20170912171912&h=d834edb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:04:11.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係電鋸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f072fda50e650efd3b0c1156a79d027bed2c882","tid":794161,"uid":167465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"好多癲線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39e3e3d215a9d99f404e62087fc5f1a78197192","tid":794161,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f9b411308970913485ec115752f93826a1224d","tid":794161,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"武士刀 vs. 遮 + 摺凳 + 空手道"},{"pid":"f103d3524bd861a40d1343110beedef961c95cf2","tid":794161,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:50:14.000Z","msg":"今次算廢左 <br />\n最勁個次係散彈槍仲要上左膛"}]}